{%- set page = 'world' -%}
{% extends "layout.html.j2" %}
{%- block meta_title -%}World{%- endblock meta_title -%}
{% block meta_description %}The World of Ishar is vast and very detailed with many areas{% endblock meta_description %}
{% block meta_url %}{{ url_for('help_page.world', _external=True) }}{% endblock meta_url %}
{% block header %}World{% endblock header %}
{%- block title -%}World{%- endblock title -%}
{%- block content %}
            <p>
                Ishar is a cohesive world with a living history.
                The vast world areas of Ishar have been written to include a detailed past that intrudes on the present,
                setting the scene for many of the adventures to be had here.
            </p>
            <p>
                From the shattered ruins of <a href="{{ url_for('help_page.single', topic='area torm sarvek') }}" title="Area: Torm Sarvek">Torm Sarvek</a>
                to the splendor of <a href="{{ url_for('help_page.single', topic='area mareldja') }}" title="Area: Mareldja">Mareldja</a>,
                the darkness of Hedros, the dense Talrynian Forest, all of these lands and more are open to you.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether treading across the barren wasteland of the Tundra or voyaging for the great Ocean, you will
                never forget the sense of wonder and discovery to be experienced here.
            </p>
    {%- if areas and areas is iterable and areas | length > 0 %}
            <ul id="world-list">
        {%- for area in areas %}
                <li title="{{ area }}">
                    <a href="{{ url_for('help_page.single', topic=area) }}">{{ area }}</a>
                </li>
        {%- endfor %}
            </ul>
    {%- endif %}
{%- endblock content %}
